Description: IIMI is short for Identifying Infection with Machine Intelligence. 
    It detects potential infected viruses from mapped plant samples and 
    visualize the mapping result of the plant samples. IIMI also provides a 
    mappability profile to eliminate unreliable regions on coverage profiles.
